source.name: FY2013 Per Diem Reimbursement Rates
source.description: The dataset contains maximum lodging reimbursement per diem rates and the meals and incidental (M&IE) rates for 392 locations across the continental United States for Fiscal Year 2013, as well as the standard per diem rates for any locations not specifically listed.
